  "text": "According to Table 4 , three of the documents proposed solutions to BMI for the farmers in the FSC in which Pölling, Sroka, and Mergenthaler [CITATION_1] consider innovation in the value proposition as a solution to BMI for the farmers. While, Varela-Candamio, Calvo, Novo-Corti [CITATION_2] , and Pölling et al. [CITATION_3] provide a new business model for the farmers in the FSC. The following is a summary of these studies.",
